body:
Last release candidate before the full release. Please help us test video calls.

## What's Changed
* chore: Raise the minor version number on feature releases. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/246
* cleanup: Reduce amount of implicit casting in signals/slots. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/249
* cleanup: Avoid contextless `connect`. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/248
* feat: Add DBus desktop notification support. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/209
* chore: Add a CI check to run the macOS distributable binary. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/250
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/247
* cleanup: Remove unnecessary inheritance of Chatroom. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/253
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/251
* feat: Add many missing emojis from the smiley packs. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/232
* cleanup: Remove duplication of widget IDs. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/252
* docs: Add more tooltips to UI settings. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/230
* chore: Build all deps including Qt statically on macOS. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/254
* chore: Add static cmake preset. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/255
* chore: Fix background and icon of macOS dmg. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/259
* cleanup: Avoid string concatenation in log output. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/258
* cleanup: Make the tongue emoji `:P` output 😛 instead of 😋. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/264
* cleanup: Ensure that all emoticons at least map to themselves. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/260
* refactor: Add logging category for tox logger output. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/265
* refactor: Add logging category to debug log. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/256
* style: Format Objective C++ files with clang-format. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/257
* cleanup: Remove unnecessary path cleaner in tox logger. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/266
* docs: Update all links to Weblate by @7K3LNAKA93W9AWRR7VZXR37N5 in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/268
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/270
* chore: Reduce flakiness of macOS builds. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/269
* chore: Support toxcore 0.2.19 and below. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/280
* cleanup: Remove most uses of `goto`. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/262
* cleanup: Use mutex lockers where possible in video frame handling. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/275
* chore: Add coverity scan static analysis. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/271
* fix: Don't crash on quit during AV call. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/274
* fix: Make camera input work again on macOS. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/267
* fix: Make sure camera access is gained on macOS before calling. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/283
* cleanup: Ensure message structs don't have uninitialised members. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/272
* fix: Disable video device selection box during call. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/284
* fix: Fix occasional deadlock in ending a video call. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/278
* chore: Use flatpak dependencies from releases instead of local paths. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/289
* cleanup: Remove unused C code. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/286
* chore: Use the same flathub manifest as flathub. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/287
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/291
* cleanup: Fix spelling mistakes in the code. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/282
* cleanup: Clarify what the "blacklist" does in privacy. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/285
* perf: Don't log verbose toxav messages. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/273
* chore: Use ccache in flatpak build. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/290
* docs: Update dependency documentation. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/279

## New Contributors
* @7K3LNAKA93W9AWRR7VZXR37N5 made their first contribution in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/268

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/compare/v1.18.0-rc.2...v1.18.0-rc.3
name: v1.18.0-rc.3
